          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-59ecd9c4ca6b51a2",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "What is the required minimum balance for a BMO AIR MILES \u00ae\u2020 Chequing Account?\nYou do not need to keep a minimum balance in the account, as long as you pay the monthly plan fee of $17.95. Plus, get 50 Bonus Miles each month you maintain a daily balance of $4,000 or more in your chequing account *106\nHow many transactions per month do I get with a BMO AIR MILES \u00ae\u2020 Chequing Account? With the BMO AIR MILES \u00ae\u2020 Chequing Account, you get unlimited transactions *52 per month. When you move money out of your account \u2013 like an ATM withdrawal, bill payment or pre-authorized payment \u2013 that counts as a transaction. Money coming into your account \u2013 like payroll direct deposits or cash deposits at an ATM \u2013 don\u2019t count as transactions.",
